From 4d9904f3626a409b267a67248f0aa070ff7eb565 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Bian Jin chen <kenjc.bian@rock-chips.com>
Date: Wed, 16 Jun 2021 19:20:41 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] services: Enable app compact by default.

Process compact need kernel process_reclaim support:
CONFIG_PROCESS_RECLAIM=y

Add rockchip native process support, sched reclaim job to reclaim native
process. Use `setprop ctl.start rockchip.reclaimd` to test.

Use `logcat -s RockchipProcessCompactor` to check detail.
Use `logcat -s RockchipReclaimD` to check native detail.

Signed-off-by: Bian Jin chen <kenjc.bian@rock-chips.com>
Change-Id: I190d9ba016afbc64bba9e1304fbd2dae916f85fd
---
